<% breadcrumb :intro %>
<section id="sl_intro_index mt-5"  data-controller="gallery">
  <article id="intro_main_content" class="row">
    <div id="sl_intro_left" class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
      <%=link_to image_tag('intro.jpg',loading: 'lazy',:alt=>'정진규'), asset_path('intro_large.jpg'), :title=>'허허허허',"data-fancybox": "gallery" %>
    </div>
    <div id="sl_intro_right" class="col-sm-12 col-md-6" itemprop="dateCreated" datetime="2024-01-02T17:00Z">
      <h3>정진규 극비 신상공개!!!</h3>
      <dl>
        <dt>이름</dt>
        <dd>정진규</dd>
        <dt>성별</dt>
        <dd>남자</dd>
        <dt>생일</dt>
        <dd>1953년 11월 2일(음력)</dd>
        <dt>직업</dt>
        <dd>은퇴자</dd>
        <dt>키</dt>
        <dd>160cm</dd>
        <dt>몸무게</dt>
        <dd>90kg</dd>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </article>
  <article class="article2 row">
    <h2 class="col-12">좋아하는것</h2>
    <p class="col-12">술,담배,여자,노래,춤등 노는것은 다 좋아함(도박도 좋아하지만 너무 못해서 못함)<br />독서,탁구,테니스,TV,낮잠,종호,버린물건 줏어오기,읽지도 않는 책 쌓아두기<br />
      <b>거짓말</b>(하지만 할때마다 걸림 ㅜ.ㅜ, 성공할때까지 나의 거짓말은 계속 될꺼야~!)</p>
  </article>
  <article class="article3 row">
    <h2 class="col-12">싫어하는것</h2>
    <p class="col-12">진실, 약속시간 맞춰가기, 남의말 듣기, 물건 버리는거, 책 버리는거(<b>사실 버려도 버렸는지도 모름</b>)</p>
  </article>
  <article class="article4 row">
    <h2 class="col-12">약력</h2>
    <dl class="col-12">
      <% unless @histories.empty? %>
      <% @histories.each do |history| %>
      <dt><%=history.year %></dt>
      <dd>
        <b><%=history.title %></b>
        <%=simple_format(history.content) %>
      <% if user_signed_in? %>
      <% if current_user.admin? %>
        <div class="history_menu">
          <%= link_to t(:edit_link), edit_history_path(history) %> &nbsp; | &nbsp; <%= link_to t(:delete_link), history, method: :delete, data: { confirm: t(:delete_confirm) } %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <% end %>
      </dd>
      <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </dl>
  <% if user_signed_in? %>
  <% if current_user.admin? %>
    <%= link_to t(:link_new), new_history_path %>
  <% end %>
  <% end %>
  </article>
</section>
<% content_for :json_ld do %>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    <%= raw(JSON.pretty_generate(json_ld_for_profile())) %>
  </script>
<% end %>